_Hi everyone!_

I am very happy to share with you the presentation of my fangame project, right here on the Pokémon Workshop website. For the back story, its development began during 2022, without any real ambitions or skills on my part. The world of game making opened its doors to me and allowed me to explore many fields through the creation of this fangame! The project is **still in development** , but a demo is planned for a date that I cannot confirm at the time of writing these lines.

_- yusiki_

## Synopsis

Play as a young boy or a young girl, originally from Kona Town, located in the west of the small Citados region where humans and Pokémon live in peace and harmony. In this beautiful region, snow falls in abundance all year round. One day, Professor Yusiki invites you to set off on a journey to conquer the region's 9 badges. Choose your first companion to begin an adventure as thrilling as it is extraordinary! But... Team Yunaï will block your path on many occasions! Very little is known about this mysterious organization, although rumors say they are looking for a mysterious regional form of Eevee... but for malicious purposes...

