## Main Features

- Side quests enriching the universe and its lore
- Unique Gym Leaders with custom gym mechanics
- New items to obtain
- Mining and resource collection in specific areas
- An animated ski resort
- A mature and immersive scenario
- Regional forms and original Fakemon
- 2v2 and 3v3 battles
- Mystery Gift and GTS

